intent.user_query: List all products along with the number of times they appear in sales details.

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT p.ProductName, COUNT(sd.ProductID) AS NumberOfTimesSold FROM fitness_db.Products p LEFT JOIN fitness_db.SaleDetails sd ON p.ProductID = sd.ProductID GROUP BY p.ProductName ORDER BY NumberOfTimesSold DESC;

arguments.sql: SELECT p.ProductName, COUNT(sd.ProductID) AS NumberOfTimesSold FROM fitness_db.Products p LEFT JOIN fitness_db.SaleDetails sd ON p.ProductID = sd.ProductID GROUP BY p.ProductName ORDER BY NumberOfTimesSold DESC;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
